{"tid":1772083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"職工盟： 反送中運動帶動新一輪「新工會浪潮」 暫已有約30組織正籌備成立","createTime":"2019-12-06T10:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T04:54:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"55e89f1842d2c3fede0bc106715ed3b6f45e8479","tid":1772083,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"近日有網民號召各行業組織工會，增加在勞工界的影響力。蒙兆達指，近月的確收到有關成立工會的查詢，試過一天內收到多個查詢電話，形容情況是他投身工會以來前所未見。據他了解，目前各行業已有約30個新工會正籌備成立，<span style=\"color: red;\">認為反送中運動帶動新一輪「新工會浪潮」。他提醒，立會勞工界議席的選民資格，要求工會成立並運作一年</span>，現時新工會將無法趕及選立會，但可以趕及特首選委投票。<span style=\"color: red;\">惟目前親建制工會數目與親民主工會數目相當懸殊，短期難改變格局</span>。吳敏兒又指，新成立的工會有心關注民主運動，對推動勞工議題有幫助。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191206/60348384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191206%2F60348384&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=15b1ecf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191206%2F60348384&h=cf10ca70\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191206/60348384</a>"},{"pid":"9124b3e4b4b682daf3750c37ae68364c4dcf7abc","tid":1772083,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2adaffff8dcaecfba8fb01d278b082463814a7b","tid":1772083,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"97a35b9fead9e154b8b53663dc1e35321a1a1752","tid":1772083,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"即係其實無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e94c27f600e2e730ff831355a42c8ea6a6d7b1","tid":1772083,"uid":38566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":